OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780326668
OL,3,CCumbria coach company backs campaign
OL,4,Cto introduce graduated driving licence
OL,6,FA Cumbrian mum is campaigning for
OL,7,Fgraduated driving licences after her
OL,8,Fdaughter died in a fatal collision in
OL,9,F2017.
OL,11,FEighteen-year-old Caitlin Huddleston
OL,12,Fdied on the A595 in West Cumbria, in a
OL,13,Fcar driven by her newly qualified
OL,14,Ffriend. According to the road safety
OL,15,Fcharity Brake, 4,740 people are killed
OL,16,For seriously injured in crashes
OL,17,Finvolving young drivers every year.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780326668
OL,3,CCumbria coach company backs campaign
OL,4,Cto introduce graduated driving licence
OL,6,FOne of the measures a Graduated
OL,7,FDriving Licence (GDL) could introduce
OL,8,Fis a restriction on 17 to 19-year-olds
OL,9,Fcarrying passengers, which AA research
OL,10,Fsuggests could save 58 lives per year.
OL,11,FA survey by Brake revealed that 77% of
OL,12,Fpeople asked want this to become law.
OL,14,FSharron Huddleston's campaign is now
OL,15,Fbeing backed by a coach company run by
OL,16,Fa director who used to be a roads
OL,17,Fpolicing officer and a collision
OL,18,Finvestigator for 15 years.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780326668
OL,3,CCumbria coach company backs campaign
OL,4,Cto introduce graduated driving licence
OL,6,FCraig Irving, Director of Irving of
OL,7,FDalston and a former traffic cop,
OL,8,Fsaid: "As a police officer, you see a
OL,9,Fnumber of horrific incidents. I think
OL,10,FSharron is doing an amazing job with
OL,11,Fthis campaign and I just wanted to
OL,12,Fsupport her. The devastation it causes
OL,13,Fto families - I think it's something
OL,14,Fthat needs to happen. It's law in
OL,15,Fplaces like Australia, so why not in
OL,16,Fthe UK?"
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780326668
OL,3,CCumbria coach company backs campaign
OL,4,Cto introduce graduated driving licence
OL,6,FHe told ITV Border: "It does affect
OL,7,Fyour mind. When you go to an inquest,
OL,8,Fafter you've investigated everything
OL,9,Fand you've got to face the family to
OL,10,Fgive your evidence, it does upset you.
OL,11,FIt really does. And especially when
OL,12,Fit's young people involved, because a
OL,13,Flot of it is avoidable. It happens on
OL,14,Fa weekly basis through peer pressure,
OL,15,Foverconfidence, and speed. I just
OL,16,Fthink it's important for Caitlin's
OL,17,Fcampaign to be introduced in the UK."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780326668
OL,3,CCumbria coach company backs campaign
OL,4,Cto introduce graduated driving licence
OL,6,FThey say other countries have seen
OL,7,Fsuccessful outcomes. GDLs introduced
OL,8,Fin Victoria, Australia, in 2007 led to
OL,9,Fa 30% reduction in fatalities by 2013.
OL,10,FNew Zealand also reported a decrease
OL,11,Fin car crash injuries following their
OL,12,Fadoption of similar measures.
OL,14,FCaitlin's mum, Sharron, has now
OL,15,Fcampaigned for Graduated Driving
OL,16,FLicences for eight years.
OL,18,F"I know that my daughter could still
OL,19,Fbe here today with me if we'd had that
OL,20,Flaw in place," she said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
