FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780326668
OL,3,CCumbria coach company backs campaign
OL,4,Cto introduce graduated driving licence
OL,6,F"It absolutely added to the
OL,7,Fdevastation to find out that for
OL,8,Fdecades before Caitlin's death, so
OL,9,Fmany bereaved families, road safety
OL,10,Fcharities, and police officers had
OL,11,Fcampaigned for this law."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780326668
OL,3,CCumbria coach company backs campaign
OL,4,Cto introduce graduated driving licence
OL,6,FSharron believes the conversation
OL,7,Fneeds to change: "In the past,
OL,8,Fgraduated driving licences have been
OL,9,Fspoken about in a negative way, using
OL,10,Flanguage like 'restricting' and
OL,11,F'preventing'. It's not that at all,
OL,12,Fit's about saving lives. What we want
OL,13,Fis our younger generation to have safe
OL,14,Fmobility wherever they go. Asking for
OL,15,Fjust that little bit of extra time to
OL,16,Fgain experience in the car, driving on
OL,17,Ftheir own or with an older,
OL,18,Fexperienced driver, is a small ask."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780326668
OL,3,CCumbria coach company backs campaign
OL,4,Cto introduce graduated driving licence
OL,6,FThe UK Government doesn't currently
OL,7,Fplan to introduce GDL measures,
OL,8,Fstating instead that they are working
OL,9,Fto keep young people safe with better
OL,10,Fpre-test preparation from a longer
OL,11,Flearning period. However, on the other
OL,12,Fside of the border, Scottish ministers
OL,13,Fwant the power to introduce the
OL,14,Flicences independently.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780326668
OL,3,CCumbria coach company backs campaign
OL,4,Cto introduce graduated driving licence
OL,6,FA Department for Transport
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Every death on our
OL,8,Froads is a tragedy, and our thoughts
OL,9,Fare with Caitlin's family. We're
OL,10,Fworking to keep young people safe
OL,11,Fwhile maintaining their access to
OL,12,Fwork, education, and social
OL,13,Fopportunities.
OL,15,F"That's why we're focusing on better
OL,16,Fpreparation before the test, and have
OL,17,Fconsulted on minimum learning periods
OL,18,Fto give learner drivers time to build
OL,19,Fessential skills."
